<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-need">in need</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在困难中；在困境中：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A friend in need is a friend indeed. 
患难见真情。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Everyone in our society should help those in need.
我们社会上的每个人都应该帮助那些有困难的人。</p><footer>2016 江苏书面表达</footer></div></div>